{"tid":144560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唐英年：候選人涵蓋不同光譜有利管治","createTime":"2017-03-05T13:21:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T13:42:39.000Z","uid":54627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f0ca4cff488d7d97f777161d4166a229f2bfdfb6","tid":144560,"uid":54627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T13:21:58.000Z","msg":"在北京，中聯辦主任張曉明被追問有否為林鄭月娥拉票，他說全屬謠言。政協常委唐英年認為，三名候選人都有一定支持，符合人大委員長張德江所指要受市民擁戴的條件，而他認為能涵蓋不同光譜將有利管治。<br />\n<br />\n正在北京的中聯辦主任張曉明，被問到有沒有干預行政長官選舉，他開腔否認。<br />\n<br />\n主管港澳事務的人大委員長張德江日前與政協委員閉門會談，講到希望選出受市民擁戴的特首。已提名林鄭月娥的政協常委唐英年說，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">候選人若涵蓋不同光譜，會更有利管治</span>。<br />\n<br />\n至於未能成功提名葉劉淑儀入閘的<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">新民黨</span>副主席田北辰，則說現階段覺得<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">曾俊華較適合當特首</span>。<br />\n<br />\n同樣沒有提名任何人的自由黨劉健儀表示，要視乎候選人政綱、辯論表現及民望才作投票決定。<br />\n<br />\n在北京開會的大部分港區政協及人大代表都是選委會成員，大部分人都提名林鄭月娥。<br />\n<br />\n風向好似唔同咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=212948\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D212948&d=5YfG332q5u5uc%2FC0Cq16Rb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=985e1f45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D212948&h=b31a5866\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=212948</a>"},{"pid":"e151162352598cc33373e2c77dfb530b9661a5c2","tid":144560,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T13:23:39.000Z","msg":"我係中共都覺薯片佬管港豬易啲㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e404332e6ad68372ea5f1bd33af59f84de4e2f44","tid":144560,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T13:23:49.000Z","msg":"泛民又中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f29f42e0ee0bcd9ff2bdbd5ab18b75a422c140","tid":144560,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T13:41:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>泛民又中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又中咩伏呀"},{"pid":"afa11dd720adbf0f253aba9ceabc186c58532759","tid":144560,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T13:42:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>泛民又中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又中咩伏呀</blockquote><br />\n泛民本身就係伏"}]}